<TIMEX3 tid="t12" type="DATE" value="2010-04-22">April 22</TIMEX3> - The Deepwater Horizon rig , valued at more than $ 560 million , sinks and a 5 - mile - long oil slick forms .
<TIMEX3 tid="t15" type="DATE" value="2010-04-25">April 25</TIMEX3> - Efforts to activate the well 's blowout preventer fail .
<TIMEX3 tid="t17" type="DATE" value="2011-04-29">April 29</TIMEX3> - U.S. President Barack Obama pledges ` ` every single available resource , '' including the U.S. military , to contain the spreading spill and says BP is responsible for the cleanup .
<TIMEX3 tid="t19" type="DATE" value="2011-04-30">April 30</TIMEX3> - An Obama aide says no drilling will be allowed in new areas , as the president had <TIMEX3 tid="t20" type="DATE" value="PAST_REF">recently</TIMEX3> proposed , until the cause of the Deepwater Horizon accident is known .
