<TIMEX3 tid="t31" type="DATE" value="2011-05-07">May 7</TIMEX3> - An attempt to place a containment dome over the spewing well fails when the device is rendered useless by frozen hydrocarbons that clogged it .
<TIMEX3 tid="t33" type="DATE" value="2011-05-09">May 9</TIMEX3> - BP says it might try to plug the undersea leak by pumping materials such as shredded tires and golf balls into the well at high pressure , a method called a ` ` junk shot . ''
<TIMEX3 tid="t34" type="DATE" value="2011-05">May</TIMEX3> 11\/12 - Executives from BP , Transocean and Halliburton appear at congressional hearings in Washington .
