<TIMEX3 tid="t43" type="DATE" value="2011-05-26">May 26</TIMEX3> - A ` ` top kill '' maneuver starts , involving pumping drilling mud and other material into the well shaft to try to stifle the flow .
<TIMEX3 tid="t45" type="DATE" value="2011-05-28">May 28</TIMEX3> - Obama tours the Louisiana coast , saying , ` ` I am the president and the buck stops with me . ''
