<TIMEX3 tid="t54" type="DATE" value="2010-06-04">June 4</TIMEX3> - Obama , on his third trip to the region , warns BP against skimping on compensation to residents and businesses .
<TIMEX3 tid="t56" type="DATE" value="2010-06-07">June 7</TIMEX3> - BP , which says it has <TIMEX3 tid="t57" type="DATE" value="PRESENT_REF">now</TIMEX3> spent $ 1.25 billion on the spill , sees shares gain on news of the progress in containing the leak .
