<TIMEX3 tid="t61" type="DATE" value="2010-06-09">June 9</TIMEX3> - U.S. Interior Secretary Ken Salazar says BP must pay the salaries of thousands of workers laid off by a moratorium on drilling , at a congressional hearing .
